    <section id="about">
        <h2>About the Program</h2>
        <p>This program empowers Detroit residents to invest in affordable housing developments through fractional ownership. It provides an opportunity to earn returns while helping to solve the housing crisis.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="how-it-works">
        <h2>How It Works</h2>
        <div class="steps">
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Fractional Ownership</h3>
                <p>Detroiters can invest in a portion of housing projects, gaining ownership in local developments.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Crowdfund Mortgages</h3>
                <p>Funding comes directly from the community, reducing the burden of traditional mortgages.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step">
                <h3>Earn Returns</h3>
                <p>Investors receive returns on their investments as developments grow and thrive.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="impact">
        <h2>Community Impact</h2>
